KitKat::

She got shot and puched off him. He had moved before she could react 
and get him. He was up in the air when she looked up and stood up.  
She put her finger in the hole in her lower chest and looked 
skyward. "For a maximal, you fight well bot. But next time, one of us 
will die."  She started to limp towards the main battle field.
